ness day.\n• We may request supporting documents through your secure client portal.\n• You\'ll receive updates at key milestones.\n\nHave questions? Just reply to this email — we\'re happy to help.\n\nYour Loan Officer\nEncore Mortgage',NULL,NULL,'sent','<enc-conv_client_180015-1775074562359@garbrix.com>',NULL,NULL,'conv_client_180015',240004,NULL,NULL,'text',28,'sent',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'2026-04-01 20:16:03','2026-04-01 20:16:03'),(360005,1,180016,NULL,NULL,NULL,180015,NULL,'email','outbound','Quick Checklist for Your Refinance (#LA73529614)','Hi Avila,\n\nGreat start! To keep your refinance moving as quickly as possible, here are the documents we\'ll need:\n\n✅ Government-issued photo ID\n✅ Last 2 months of pay stubs\n✅ Last 2 years of W-2s or tax returns\n✅ Last 2–3 months of bank statements\n✅ Most recent mortgage statement\n✅ Homeowners insurance declaration page\n\nUpload them securely through your client portal whenever you\'re ready. Getting ahead on documents can save days in processing.\n\nQuestions? We\'re a reply or call away.\n\nYour Loan Officer\nEncore Mortgage',NULL,NULL,'sent','<enc-conv_client_180015-1775075525257@garbrix.com>',NULL,NULL,'conv_client_180015',240004,NULL,NULL,'text',29,'sent',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'2026-04-01 20:32:05','2026-04-01 20:32:05'),(390005,1,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'sms','inbound',NULL,'Hey Elizabeth, my name is Cade and I’m a recruiter with Barrett Financial Group. I was reviewing your production from last year and honestly thought you’d be a great fit here.\n\nBarrett has been around for 20+ years and supports over 2,000 loan officers nationwide, so the model is very dialed in for originators. It’s simple: a flat $695 per file. No splits, no percentages, no company caps. Most LOs who make the switch end up doubling or even tripling their take-home within their first year.\n\nWe’re big on support. Our LOs have access to processing and LOA teams, marketing, sales managers, and a help desk, all built to keep your focus on originating. We’re also 1099 and give you the freedom to build your own team and brand.\n\nWith over $10B funded last year, the model has proven itself. Who’s to say it wouldn’t work well for you 😉 If you’re already self-sourcing and doing 12+ deals a year, it’s kind of a no-brainer. Let me know what time works best this week to hop on a call.\nReply STOP to unsubscribe',NULL,NULL,'delivered','SMe837f95d95ac7e8a1d3e96af6bf41d57',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'text',NULL,'delivered',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'2026-04-01 22:12:13','2026-04-01 22:12:13'),(420005,1,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'sms','inbound',NULL,'Hola Nery soy Fernando te conocí en el  avión ',NULL,NULL,'delivered','SMec0b5768abd700bededdc02d573c6ca2',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'text',NULL,'delivered',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'2026-04-02 11:51:51','2026-04-02 11:51:51'),(420007,1,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'sms','inbound',NULL,'Este es mi número ',NULL,NULL,'delivered','SM68cbefc7bacf9691ce47edfbe7de3d01',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'text',NULL,'delivered',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'2026-04-02 11:51:56','2026-04-02 11:51:56'),(420009,1,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'sms','inbound',NULL,'Tienes WhatsApp?',NULL,NULL,'delivered','SM8745ed92bb3442c1944d1e067793c4b0',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'text',NULL,'delivered',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'2026-04-02 11:52:02','2026-04-02 11:52:02'),(420011,1,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'sms','inbound',NULL,'Van a venir por ti o como te vas a ir ? Por si gustas en aventon con gueto te puedo llevar ',NULL,NULL,'delivered','SMe18dca161c742568406f3aea26fc5b1c',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'text',NULL,'delivered',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'2026-04-02 11:52:47','2026-04-02 11:52:47'),(450005,1,180016,NULL,NULL,NULL,180015,NULL,'sms','outbound',NULL,'Hi Avila, Your Loan Officer here from Encore Mortgage. Just checking in on your refinance app (#LA73529614). Have you had a chance to review your document checklist in the portal? We\'re here to help make this easy!',NULL,NULL,'sent','SM302f54fcdaec37395b9acd05e2910b4c',NULL,NULL,'conv_client_180015',240004,NULL,NULL,'text',30,'sent',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,0.0000,NULL,NULL,NULL,'2026-04-03 20:48:04','2026-04-03 20:48:04'),(480005,1,NULL,NULL,NULL,3,150015,NULL,'sms','outbound',NULL,'Hola',NULL,NULL,'sent','SMb0d2e7731bd97d4e608d0524a489c7f2',NULL,NULL,'conv_client_150015',NULL,NULL,NULL,'text',NULL,'sent',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'{\"direction\": \"outbound-api\", \"sid\": \"SMb0d2e7731bd97d4e608d0524a489c7f2\", \"status\": \"queued\", \"uri\": \"/2010-04-01/Accounts/ACXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXXX/Messages/SMb0d2e7731bd97d4e608d0524a489c7f2.json\"}',NULL,NULL,'2026-04-04 14:46:03','2026-04-04 14:46:03'),(480007,1,NULL,NULL,NULL,3,150015,NULL,'call','outbound',NULL,'📞 Voice call — 0s (completed)',NULL,NULL,'sent',NULL,NULL,NULL,'conv_client_150015',NULL,NULL,NULL,'text',NULL,'sent',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'2026-04-04 14:46:34','2026-04-04 14:46:34'),(480009,1,NULL,NULL,NULL,3,150015,NULL,'call','outbound',NULL,'📞 Voice call — 12s (completed)',NULL,NULL,'sent','CA2706acd377e2709a47f58320eac3b462',NULL,NULL,'conv_client_150015',NULL,NULL,NULL,'text',NULL,'sent',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'2026-04-04 14:46:34','2026-04-04 14:46:34'),(480011,1,NULL,NULL,NULL,3,150015,NULL,'call','outbound',NULL,'📞 Voice call — 14s (completed)',NULL,NULL,'sent','CA52cfa546af250e7ed0764c3f5fa5ed86',NULL,NULL,'conv_client_150015',NULL,NULL,NULL,'text',NULL,'sent',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'2026-04-04 14:47:35','2026-04-04 14:47:35'),(480013,1,NULL,NULL,NULL,3,150015,NULL,'call','outbound',NULL,'📞 Voice call — 0s (completed)',NULL,NULL,'sent',NULL,NULL,NULL,'conv_client_150015',NULL,NULL,NULL,'text',NULL,'sent',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'2026-04-04 14:47:35','2026-04-04 14:47:35'),(510005,1,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'sms','inbound',NULL,'Although Barrett is headquartered in AZ, we’re licensed in 49 states. As long as you’re properly licensed through NMLS, you can do business nationwide. And for any one-off out-of-state deals, our referral team can take the file and pay you 100 bps at close. If that aligns with how you operate, happy to set up a quick convo 🙂\n\nCade Ellingson | Barrett Financial Group',NULL,NULL,'delivered','SM6d1b3d87e763bc906c84050943bd5a4e',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'text',NULL,'delivered',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'2026-04-06 16:23:11','2026-04-06 16:23:11'),(540005,1,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'sms','inbound',NULL,'We keep our LOS simple - we use ARIVE. It\'s built for efficiency with clean workflows, easy borrower uploads, and faster closings. Our top 30 lenders are integrated into ARIVE\'s pricing engine, so you can shop live rates and choose borrower-paid, lender-paid, or correspondent comp per deal.\n\nIf you\'d like, we can hop on a Zoom call to walk through the system and compare pricing & comp apples to apples. I\'d love to hear your thoughts Elizabeth, just let me know!',NULL,NULL,'delivered','SM561f7f4f0216de0921a7a78954a77718',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'text',NULL,'delivered',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'2026-04-08 16:13:52','2026-04-08 16:13:52'),(570005,1,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'sms','inbound',NULL,'Hi Elizabeth, this is Jonathan Rhoden with United Mortgage. I’d love to connect and show you how to own your mortgage branch. Call me back or visit Branch.UnitedMtg.net. - Talk soon!\n',NULL,NULL,'delivered','SM30c2de242e258f4759cb8104b1c1e08e',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'text',NULL,'delivered',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'2026-04-08 21:25:16','2026-04-08 21:25:16'),(600005,1,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'sms','inbound',NULL,'How\'s it going Elizabeth? I know that with every individual borrower come very individual needs, and you don\'t always have access to a product to suit those needs. \n\nAt Barrett we work with over 170 lender partners and 12 correspondent lenders. This allows us to broker every loan type under the sun amaking your job as an LO easier and giving you no shortage of options to assist your borrower. \n\nIf it makes sense, I\'m happy to set up a brief call to walk through our lender list and answer any questions you may have. When can we connect?',NULL,NULL,'delivered','SM4fd388d607fdd143db3f352f7545bc65',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'text',NULL,'delivered',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'2026-04-09 16:13:36','2026-04-09 16:13:36'),(630005,1,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'call','inbound',NULL,'📞 Incoming call from +15623499638',NULL,NULL,'sent','CA64c8b1d7c98c3991d7e0e46376e134c1',NULL,NULL,'conv_phone_15623499638',NULL,NULL,NULL,'text',NULL,'sent',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'2026-04-09 17:16:35','2026-04-09 17:16:35'),(660005,1,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'call','inbound',NULL,'📞 Incoming call from +13234756240',NULL,NULL,'sent','CA2f2a080c8552ab3e664e0eb6010e2874',NULL,NULL,'conv_phone_13234756240',NULL,NULL,NULL,'text',NULL,'sent',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'2026-04-09 18:59:56','2026-04-09 18:59:56'),(720005,1,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'call','inbound',NULL,'📞 Incoming call from +15622613857',NULL,NULL,'sent','CAd7982d087a269ffb4643cabdb7ffa03a',NULL,NULL,'conv_phone_15622613857',NULL,NULL,NULL,'text',NULL,'sent',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'2026-04-09 19:44:00','2026-04-09 19:44:00'),(750005,1,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'call','inbound',NULL,'📞 Incoming call from +14789930605',NULL,NULL,'sent','CAfe291cc0878871f2b9e252b26dbad599',NULL,NULL,'conv_phone_14789930605',NULL,NULL,NULL,'text',NULL,'sent',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'2026-04-09 20:46:40','2026-04-09 20:46:40'),(810005,1,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'call','inbound',NULL,'📞 Incoming call from +15622613857',NULL,NULL,'sent','CA4e2cd73edbe6f5f4596d83534a1f6606',NULL,NULL,'conv_phone_15622613857',NULL,NULL,NULL,'te